BAIL HEARING - 
Defendant in custody and appearing by video from the Manitowoc County Jail.  The State informs the Court that the defendant will be charged with the crime of possess THC, 2nd subsequent, 5 cts. threat to law enforcement officer, 2 cts discharge bodily fluids, resist arrest.  The matter is continued for initial appearance on 07-11-22 at 1:30 p.m.  Bail is set at $250.00 cash bond. Bail not furnished and defendant is remanded to the custody of the Sheriff.
